sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Agent as AI Agent<br/>(Claude)
    participant MCP as MCP Server<br/>:8085/mcp
    participant Intent as Intent Parser<br/>Middleware
    participant FGA as FGA Auth<br/>Middleware
    participant Anthropic as Anthropic API<br/>(claude-haiku-4-5)
    participant OpenFGA as OpenFGA<br/>:8080
    participant Tool as Tool Handler<br/>(list-team / list-salaries)

    User->>Agent: "Show me the team" /<br/>"Show me salaries"
    Agent->>MCP: POST /mcp<br/>x-api-key: alice<br/>x-user-intent: "Show me the team"<br/>body: tools/call { name: "list-team" }

    MCP->>Intent: forward request

    alt x-user-intent header present
        Intent->>Anthropic: Does calling list-team serve<br/>"Show me the team"?
        Anthropic-->>Intent: { "allowed": true, "reason": "..." }
    end

    alt intent not aligned
        Intent-->>Agent: 403 Forbidden
    else intent aligned (or no intent header)
        Intent->>FGA: forward request

        FGA->>FGA: extract user → "agent:alice"
        FGA->>OpenFGA: Check: agent:alice can_use tool:list-team
        OpenFGA-->>FGA: { "allowed": true }

        alt not allowed
            FGA-->>Agent: 403 Forbidden
        else allowed
            FGA->>Tool: forward request
            Tool-->>FGA: team member data
            FGA-->>Intent: response
            Intent-->>MCP: response
            MCP-->>Agent: tool result
            Agent-->>User: formatted response
        end
    end
